<h3 id="toc0"><span>RAISA REVISION FILTRATOR:</span></h3>
<p><em>Revisions Have Been Highlighted, Redundant Information Omitted</em></p>
</div>
<p><strong>Item:</strong> SCP-4704</p>
<p><strong>Object Class:</strong> <span style="color: blue">Euclid</span></p>
<p><strong>Special Containment Procedure:</strong> <span style="color: blue">All SCP-4704 instances are to be transported to storage containment hangar 92-Δ of Area-92 located in Talamanca, Costa Rica. All personnel currently associated to SCP-4704 research team are now assigned to Area-92. HDD<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup> monitors remain active within these buildings at all times. If a fluctuation in Hume level is detected, agents are to pin-point instances responsible and remove them for examination.</span></p>
<p><strong>Description:</strong></p>
<p><span style="color: blue">When several instances are simultaneously activated, designated a cluster-activation<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-2" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-2')">2</a></sup>, combined frequencies emitted will increase in strength. Cluster-activations produce significant hume field discrepancies, and the resulting modifications are severe, affecting a radius of up to 4000 meters. Recorded alterations include:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="color: blue">Rapid growth of vegetation native to the South American region including many species of flora, trees, and foliage.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: blue">Terrain deformation and seismic activity of a maximum magnitude of 7-8.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: blue">Violent atmospheric disturbance and inconsistent meteorological shifts, usually resulting in tropical storms.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: blue">Atmospheric and sedimentary purification.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: blue">Gradual accumulation of anomalously manifested fresh water into a large singular body.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="color: blue">Changes persist despite the cease of sonorous stimulation and are non reversible via standard methods.</span></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: blue">Addendum 4704.01:</span></strong> Test Log-064</p>
<p>The following is the first successfully recorded cluster-activation. After an extensive operation to publicly conceal incident, containment of SCP-4704 has been adjusted, including the construction of subterranean specialized containment area designated Area-92 to house all known instances of SCP-4704, and function as hub for SCP-4704 research team.</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>4704 TEST LOG-164:</strong><br />
<strong>Subjects Tested:</strong> 4704-048, 4704-004, 4704-113<br />
<strong>Position Adjustment:</strong> SCP-4704-004 rotated 45° clockwise from prior position<br />
<strong>Object #:</strong> 028<br />
<strong>Object:</strong> Wooden Flute With Internal Wind Channel Of Native American Craft<br />
<strong>Procedure:</strong> D-15302 instructed to enter test chamber containing SCP-4704-048, -004, and -113 positioned in a acute triangle. D-15302 instructed to approach the center of containment chamber and to play a constant High G note.<br />
<strong>Effects:</strong><br />
<em>00:00:45</em>- Foliage completely overtakes chamber floor and walls.<br />
<em>00:01:20</em>- Instances of <em>Cedrela odorata</em><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-3" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-3')">3</a></sup> and <em>Schizolobium parahyba</em><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-4" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-4')">4</a></sup> sprout through floor and rapidly mature, penetrating roof of chamber.<br />
<em>00:02:02</em>- Terrain of site begins to shift.<br />
<em>00:02:10</em>- D-15302 has ceased playing High G note, however alterations continue.<br />
<em>00:03:15</em>- Foliage beings to extend to rest of facility.<br />
<em>00:06:10</em>- Foliage extends to exterior of site and beyond.<br />
<em>00:06:32</em>- Weather patterns begin to fluctuate, producing heavy winds and rain.<br />
<em>00:06:58</em>- Small body of water begins to generate 1000&#160;m the north of site.<br />
<em>00:07:13</em>- Region experiences seismic tremor.<br />
<em>00:07:49</em>- Seismic disturbances result in small protruding rupture of terrain within facility.<br />
<em>00:08:01</em>- Smoke escapes from rupture.<br />
<em>00:08:09</em>- D-15302 ordered to displace SCP-4704 instances<br />
<em>00:08:13</em>- D-15302 does as instructed. Modifications subside.</p>
<p><strong>Results:</strong> Damage to structural integrity of Site 92. SCP-4704 affecting public vicinity. Containment breach of SCP-████ , SCP-████ , SCP-████ , and SCP-████.</p>
</blockquote>
