<h3 id="toc1"><span>RAISA REVISION FILTRATOR:</span></h3>
<p><em>Revisions Have Been Highlighted, Redundant Information Omitted</em></p>
</div>
<p><strong>Item #:</strong> SCP-4704</p>
<p><strong>Object Class:</strong> Euclid</p>
<p><strong>Special Containment Procedure:</strong></p>
<p><span style="color: blue">SCP-4704-ö̀ is to be kept in standard containment chamber of Area-42 also outfitted with a single SRA.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-5" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-5')">5</a></sup>. SCP-4704-ö̀ does not require sustenance. In the event of SCP-4704-ö̀ breaching from chamber, security personnel are to record all actions of the subject, but make no aggressive response. If SCP-4704-ö̀ makes contact with SCP-4704 instances, security are not to respond with hostility and to prepare facility evacuation procedures. When conversing with SCP-4704-ö̀, information involving the Foundation is considered classified and not to be disclosed despite the subject's persistence.</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="color: blue"><strong>Researcher Note:</strong></span> Pardon my frankness, but I feel this should be said directly. This, if anything, can be considered an unorthodox method of containment, but an effective one. The anchors are mostly for show. Yes, they have some effect on SCP-4704-ö̀, but its understanding of hume field manipulation far exceeds our own. It is difficult to compete with an entity for which the bending of reality it seems is almost like a hobby. If SCP-4704-ö̀ wished to leave the site, there is very little we can do to prevent it at this time. The only real leverage we have over this entity is its apparent fascination with aspects of human society, and to a greater degree, of us. Humor it, answer its questions, be polite, take notes. If we play our roles correctly, then we may just learn a thing or two.</p>
<p>Besides, as long as we have the stones, we have the monkey.</p>
<p>- <em>Dr. Rodolfo, Lead Researcher</em></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Description:</strong></p>
<p><span style="color: blue">SCP-4704-ö̀ is a sentient organic entity capable of altering the cellular composition of itself to an undocumented maximum degree and which currently resembles a male <em>Cebus capucinus</em><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-6" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-6')">6</a></sup>. This entity demonstrates a high level of intelligence and is able to communicate through speech, despite the psychical limitations of its corporeal form. Additionally, SCP-4704-ö̀ demonstrates a resistance to the effects of hume field manipulation, capable of altering itself in spite of the presence of SRAs. It is currently theorized this is due to SCP-4704-ö̀'s form maintaining its own hume field which it manipulates freely without affecting surrounding hume fields. All these prior factors have made effectively containing SCP-4704-ö̀ untenable. However, SCP-4704-ö̀ has been cooperative with the Foundation and has agreed to refrain from causing public disturbance. In return, SCP-4704-ö̀ has requested frequent conversations with personnel, as well as access to SCP-4704 instances for the purpose of demonstrations.</span></p>
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/inbox/Monkey"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/inbox/Monkey/medium.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="Monkey" class="image" /></a>
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>SCP-4704-ö̀ answering researcher questions during a demonstration</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><span style="color: blue">SCP-4704-ö̀ has extensive knowledge of the nature of SCP-4704, claiming to be their source of origin. Though the foundation has no method of validating this claim, historical information offered by SCP-4704-ö̀ as well as its skill in the utilization of SCP-4704 suggest the claim is legitimate.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-7" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-7')">7</a></sup> SCP-4704-ö̀ will often ask questions concerning history, recent events, economic or social status of individuals, and details of the Foundation's purpose.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: blue">SCP-4704-ö̀ frequently preforms demonstrations of SCP-4704's capabilities, claiming that it wishes to educate the Research Personnel. Since SCP-4704-ö̀'s arrival SCP-4704 instances have been recorded to produce the following additional effects:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="color: blue">Rapid generation of foliage with no limitation of global region</span></li>
<li><span style="color: blue">Atmospheric temperature alteration of no known maximum degree (decrease or increase)</span></li>
<li><span style="color: blue">Alteration of surrounding surface area to the form of dried out soil, fertile soil, obsidian, coral, marble, solid ice, glass, concrete, wood, steel, an unknown sponge like substance, etc.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: blue">Generation of self-originated fire, volcanic rock, sterile water, salt water, mist, dust particles, static electricity, and plasma</span></li>
<li><span style="color: blue">Creation and rapid development of single cell organisms (hypothesized that if activation is indefinitely sustained ████ ██████ ███████ █████████)</span></li>
<li><span style="color: blue">████████████ within inorganic and organic subjects inside area of effect</span></li>
<li><span style="color: blue">Complete ██████████████ ██ █████████ ███ ███████ inside area of effect</span></li>
</ul>
<p><sub><span style="color: blue">For in-depth record and analysis of spacial positioning and tones utilized by<br />
SCP-4704-ö̀ in order to produce the prior effects, please refer to the <em>&quot;4704-Position to Tone Relation Guide Volume 02&quot;</em></span></sub></p>
<p><span style="color: blue"><strong>Addendum 4704.01:</strong></span> Incident Report SCP-4704-ö̀</p>
<p>SCP-4704-ö̀ first came to the attention of the Foundation by his own accord on 11/03/11. SCP-4704-ö̀ entered Area-92, anomalously manifesting into storage containment hangar 92-Δ, triggering HDD monitors and notifying personnel of intrusion. SCP-4704-ö̀ began to interact with SCP-4704 instances until arrival of security personnel. Though firearms appeared to have no effect on SCP-4704-ö̀, the entity calmly obeyed instructions, speaking in an indiscernible language. SCP-4704-ö̀ was then held in an improvised containment chamber, as none were originally necessary in Area-92.</p>
<p><span style="color: blue"><strong>Addendum 4704.02:</strong></span> Following the prior incident, it was soon discovered that SCP-4704-ö̀ speaks a tonal SOV language of the Chibchan family, spoken by some tribes of the indigenous Costa Rican population. Upon this discovery, a translator of said language was brought on site from the Foundation's Linguistic Division. The following interview was conducted by said researcher upon his arrival.</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Interviewed:</strong> SCP-4704-ö̀</p>
<p><strong>Interviewer:</strong> Dr. Muñoz</p>
<p><strong>Foreword:</strong> Transcription translated to English.</p>
<p><strong>&lt;Begin Log&gt;</strong></p>
<p><strong>Dr. Muñoz:</strong> Hello</p>
<p><em>Subject does not respond. Appears to be inspecting a small object.</em></p>
<p><strong>Dr. Muñoz:</strong> Hello?</p>
<p><strong>SCP-4704-ö̀:</strong> Ah, sorry. You speak Bribri?</p>
<p><strong>Dr. Rodolfo:</strong> Yes. What is that?</p>
<p><strong>SCP-4704-ö̀:</strong> Don't know. You should. In your weapons.</p>
<p><strong>Dr. Rodolfo:</strong> A bullet?</p>
<p><strong>SCP-4704-ö̀:</strong> &lt;Bulit&gt;? Small, but hurts.</p>
<p><strong>Dr. Muñoz:</strong> Yes, I apologize-</p>
<p><em>Subject smiles.</em></p>
<p><strong>SCP-4704-ö̀:</strong> Don't. Don't. I like new. There is much new, for me. I've been gone. Long time.</p>
<p><strong>Dr. Muñoz:</strong> Gone? Gone where?</p>
<p><strong>SCP-4704-ö̀:</strong> Too long, but returned now. Thank you.</p>
<p><strong>Dr. Muñoz:</strong> I don't understand.</p>
<p><strong>SCP-4704-ö̀:</strong> You use stones, yes?<br />
<br />
<strong>Dr. Muñoz:</strong> I believe we did. You know what they are then?</p>
<p><strong>SCP-4704-ö̀:</strong> Yes, yes, my stones. Bring me back. Yes. Glad to be back.</p>
<p><strong>Dr. Rodolfo:</strong> You claim them?</p>
<p><strong>SCP-4704-ö̀:</strong> I made them, so they are mine. My stones. I am Sibú. Yes, that's me. Creator of stones.<br />
<br />
<strong>Dr. Muñoz:</strong> Wait you- you are-</p>
<p><strong>SCP-4704-ö̀:</strong> Yes, yes, Sibú. Creator of man. Creator of Earth. That's me. I'm back. Your use, eh no, worship, your worship of my stones returned me.</p>
<p><em>Dr. Muñoz pauses</em></p>
<p><strong>Dr. Muñoz:</strong> I don't- I'm sorry. Sibú was a man, no?</p>
<p><strong>SCP-4704-ö̀:</strong> Disguise. Needed disguise. Weak, also. Both. Disguised and weak. Weak without worship.</p>
<p><strong>Dr. Muñoz:</strong> I see. So, our music, that was worship to you?</p>
<p><em>Subject appears thoughtful. Subject then laughs and tilts head.</em></p>
<p><strong>SCP-4704-ö̀:</strong> Yes! Music! Music&#8230; Yes. Need music for the worship, do my miracles through stone. You worship me, keep worshiping me, I help you more. More miracles.<br />
<br />
<strong>Dr. Muñoz:</strong> Well, we'll have to consider that. We are not in a position to promise more, um, worship.</p>
<p><strong>SCP-4704-ö̀:</strong> Grateful anyways! You, [ <em>Subject points to Dr. Rodolfo, who had been watching the proceedings.</em> ] you remember where you come from. You remember, so I show you how to worship. Do many things. Do anything. You already saw.<br />
<br />
<br />
<strong>&lt;End Log&gt;</strong></p>
<p><strong>Closing Statement:</strong> Behavior of SCP-4704-ö̀ during interview leaves researches uncertain of its sincerity. Despite this, request to continue testing with assistance of SCP-4704-ö̀ was authorized by O5 council, which lead to discovery of numerous additional effects.</p>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="color: blue"><strong>Addendum 4704.02:</strong></span> Findings Report</p>
<p>The following is a report on research carried out by lead researcher Dr. Rodolfo into the origin and possible nature of SCP-4704-ö̀.</p>
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/inbox/Sibu"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/inbox/Sibu/medium.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="Sibu" class="image" /></a>
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>Articulated gold pendant representing Sibú with the head of an eagle. Pre-Columbian Gold Museum, San José Costa Rica.</p>
</div>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Analysis of Costa Rican Historical Context in Relation to SCP-4704</span></strong><br />
L. Rodolfo, Lead Researcher, Area-92</p>
<p>I find it pertinent to note that following my assignment to SCP-4704, I performed independent research into the the local Mesoamerican tribes of the Diquis Delta province. During this research I stumbled upon the name Sibú in context to a hero and creation deity figure. However, I did not initially find this information relevant to our studies of SCP-4704 effects. With the appearance of a reality bending entity claiming to be said deity, I have decided preform an in depth investigation of this legend with the assistance of The Folklore/Mythology Unit (FMU) of the Field Research Department.<br />
<br />
This subject was said to be a member of an ancient demon race, titled the Sòrburu, which ruled the Earth prior to man. Sibú confronted and defeated his own people, taking reign over the Earth and becoming the principal deity of this mythology. Sibú then began to shape the planet itself, giving it a new form to his liking. There is the presence of objects titled &quot;magical rocks&quot; throughout this legend and it carries thematic similarities to SCP-4704's anomalous nature.</p>
<p>I believe this story and the newly arrived entity to, at the very least, speak some notion of the truth. The relationship between SCP-4704-ö̀ and the ancient civilizations is as of yet unclear, but we can be certain SCP-4704 are of its creation.</p>
</blockquote>
<p><iframe src="/inbox/html/b2e5b84994dc0bbe3e659d9f8b63933e29eddd02-1286774148943207965" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
</div>
