<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2><span><span style="color: black">BY ORDER OF THE OVERSEER COUNCIL</span></span></h2>
<p><span style="color: black">Access to this file restricted to personnel with Level 4 or higher Delta (Δ) clearance set. Attempt to access file without necessary clearance will be logged and result in immediate disciplinary action.</span></p>
</div>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: black">4704</span></strong></p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
</div>
<div style="border:solid 1px #999999; background:#f2f2c2; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><em>Following the neutralization of SCP-4704, clearance requisites for access to this file have been lifted by <strong>The O5 Council</strong> and <strong>The Records And Information Security Administration</strong> on 02\29\2016</em></p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>Special Containment Procedure:</strong> <span style="color: blue">All research personnel assigned to Area-92 are required to possess a copy of the <em>4704-Position to Tone Relation Guide Volume 5</em> as supplied by on site database. Activation of instances for use in the Delta Enclosure Project requires Level 5-Δ clearance and authorization of 4704 Lead Researcher. Personnel assigned to Area-92 must regularly undergo a reality-dissonance psych assessment.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-9" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-9')">9</a></sup> Personnel given Level 4/5-Δ clearance must take a RPR Examination<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-10" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-10')">10</a></sup> and undergo a 1 month background check of antecedent assignments.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: blue">SCP-4704-ö̀ has been given authorization to operate as a consultant during the construction of additional ████████ ██████████ ██████████ (███).<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-11" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-11')">11</a></sup></span></p>
<p><strong>Description:</strong> <span style="color: blue">SCP-4704-ö̀ has shown to be capable of altering the cellular composition of itself to an unlimited degree, changing its corporeal form often. Its forms usually consist of local wild life, and a human male of seemingly Latin American descent. SCP-4704-ö̀ has also been able to adeptly learn a multitude of modern languages and expressions.</span></p>
<p><iframe src="/inbox/html/6d163fc736661cb06e59fec02bf2f24c053e3b31-178698888407041790" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<p><span style="color: blue"><strong>Addendum 4704.01:</strong></span> Containment Committee Proposal</p>
<blockquote>
